# Version control & local tooling
.git
.github
.claude
.mcp.json

# Dependencies & build output (rebuilt cleanly inside each build stage)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build

# Secrets — never bake into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Docs / build files not needed at runtime
*.md
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
compose*.yaml

# Dev-only source
backend/tests
backend/requests
backend/compose.yaml
